<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any =
questions which you may have in relation to any of the specific items in th=
e tender comparison, please do not hesitate to ask.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Our =
recommendation is to settle the structural claim based on the most competit=
ive tender response provided by JLG. $419,434.08 Incl GST.<o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I lo=
ok forward to further correspondence and receiving the findings from your i=
