<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hell=
o All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Refe=
rring to your email below of December 9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Are =
you able to indicate the status of the undertaking of your independent inve=
stigations as proposed below.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We h=
ave received 3 tender responses back from the reinstatement service provide=
rs who attended site with Raffaella and myself late last year.<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As w=
e are all aware we have received these tender responses based on the scope =
of works provided by ASURNZ and subsequently shared with all parties.<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Agre=
ement on the scope of works is paramount to claim progression. If we can mo=
ve to determine the agreed scope for claim related loss =E2=80=93 we can mo=
ve quickly afterwards to provide the final outcome.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I lo=
ok forward to an update on your independent enquiries.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Than=
k you very much.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rega=
rds,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Gran=
t. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
