<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">It w=
ould be a significant progression if I could work with tender respondents a=
nd begin the tendering process before the beginning of the Christmas break.=
