sponse to the findings of all the documents attached.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Whil=
e you are reviewing the attachments, I would like to propose that I begin t=
he process of obtaining repair proposals from Tower approved builders to pr=
ogress the claim as quickly as possible.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If I=
 send out the scope of works now and offer to meet with the tender responde=
nts onsite, we may well have some preliminary costings to hand prior to the=
 end of the business year.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Plea=
se confirm your approval for me to begin the process of preliminary pricing=
 now.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
