cm 0cm 0cm">
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;fo=
nt-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">From:</span></b><span class=3D"ap=
ple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-fa=
mily:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-U=
S" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Gr=
ant
 Metson &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.=
co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Sent:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Tuesday, 14 =
October 2025 4:51 PM<br>
<b>To:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Raffaella del =
Prete &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud.com<=
/a>&gt;<br>
<b>Cc:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Abigail Collin=
 &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Abigail.Collin@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Abigail.Collin@wy=
nnwilliams.co.nz</a>&gt;; Richard Hargreaves &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Richard.=
Hargreaves@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Richard.Hargreaves@wynnwilliams.co.nz</a>&gt=
;;
 Bryan Strong &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Bryan.Strong@tower.co.nz">Bryan.Strong@=
tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Kelly Mason &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Kelly.Mason@tower.co=
.nz">Kelly.Mason@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Arna Neems &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Arna=
.Neems@tower.co.nz">Arna.Neems@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Lance
 O'Riley &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Lance.ORiley@tower.co.nz">Lance.ORiley@tower=
.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>RE: C9030=
6048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE.FID3167762]</span><span=
 lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hell=
o Raffaella,</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Than=
k you for the email below.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We c=
an confirm that testing can commence at 2pm on Friday October 17.</span><sp=
an lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We w=
ill test from sample sites as required to complete a full and thorough dete=
rmination of any potential contamination, inclusive of all the areas which =
you have referred to below.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You =
may undertake your own independent testing at any stage; however, Tower wou=
ld only consider reimbursement for testing which is - a) claim related &amp=
; b) testing which is outside of that which
 Tower will complete.<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></s=
pan><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am=
 confident that the Tower Insurance testing will be transparent, quantified=
 by lab results, and adequate to provide comfort for all parties.</span><sp=
an lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">C=
larified scope of testing as follows:</span></u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;ms=
o-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">150mm diameter inspection p=
ortals cut in wall cavities of every room on the first floor at a height of=
 300 mm of floor level and directly underneath the top plate.</span><span l=
ang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=
=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the roof cavity =
at the soffit junction where potential contaminants may have risen through =
the wall cavity. Testing of the roof cavity at the apex where smoke may hav=
e accumulated.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=
=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l1=
0 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the underside of=
 the rear large upper deck.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></=
li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm=
;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the basement uti=
lizing all exposed framing cavities and 150mm testing portals cut into any =
remining ceiling linings in the basemen area.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o=
:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm=
;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any additional sample sites=
 that we feel are required during testing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span l=
ang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">T=
o ensure effectual testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the =
following:</span></u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;ms=
o-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was locat=
ed in the laundry room downstairs at the time of the fire.</span><span lang=
=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"m=
argin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The quantity of the chlorin=
e that was in that room at the time of the fire.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"=
><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:=
0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Where there any<span class=
=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>other chemicals</u><span class=
=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that were located in that same room=
, or anywhere else downstairs. &nbsp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p=
></span></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Beyo=
nd completing testing and providing laboratory results as described above, =
I am certain the most productive action we can make towards progressing the=
 claim is to have a meeting where we can
 discuss the overall claim response process, providing a forum for you to t=
able any questions, or concerns that you may hold. Those concerns can be re=
sponded to, and the responses can be documented via minutes with actions an=
d agreements detailed in the minutes
 providing a framework for moving forward with a pre-agreed and productive =
pathway. I believe this would be very worthwhile and will provide us all wi=
th detail, clarity, and documentation that we can all use to our benefit.</=
span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Your=
 lawyers and advisors would of course be welcome to attend this meeting.</s=
pan><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I lo=
ok forward to seeing you again on Friday.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Kind=
 Regards,</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Gran=
t. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-=
