</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The =
intention is to test for smoke and chemical contamination within the wall c=
avities, and on the exposed surfaces downstairs. There will be a significan=
t number of sample sites [tests] to be
 completed to be able to author a reliable report. After initial testing is=
 completed, our intention is to apply restorative cleaning methods to targe=
ted individual sample sites, followed by subsequent testing, post-cleaning,=
 to provide data to measure the
 effectiveness of cleaning/decontamination.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All =
samples taken from site will require laboratory analysis before being incor=
porated into a report. This process may take up to 10 working days =E2=80=
=93 so we want to capture swab samples from surfaces
 before and after the decontamination process is undertaken.</span><span la=
ng=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">At t=
his stage we are looking like being able to conduct this testing onsite, as=
 well as CPEng site visit for assessment, on Friday October 17. Time to yet=
 be confirmed.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am=
